caption: b'May this festive season fill your home with joy and peace.  Merry Christmas and Happy Holidays to you!\n\nFor this and other #SQSpotify playlists, visit SIA\xe2\x80\x99s Spotify page.'

b"Thank you for joining us at our Inside Singapore Airlines event! Here are some moments we love from the exclusive tours at our training centre yesterday. We hope you're enjoying #DiscoverYourSIA! :airplane:"

b"We can\xe2\x80\x99t wait to welcome you Inside Singapore Airlines tomorrow! If you can't be there in person, look out for our Instagram Stories for our event coverage at the SIA Training Centre from 0900hrs (SGT). Stay tuned! #DiscoverYourSIA"
b'As we welcome the festival of lights once again, we hope it will brighten every home around the world :sparkles: Happy Deepavali!'

b"We care about the health and safety of our customers and staff. With the extra precautions we're taking to keep our cabins clean, you can expect a safe and comfortable journey when you next join us on board. #SIAcares\n\nLearn more about Our Promise of Care at bit.ly/SIACOVID19Measures"

b'It has been such an exciting day for all of us at Restaurant A380 @changiairport ! Thank you for joining us. For those of you participating in the later sessions, we look forward to seeing you! \n\n#DiscoverYourSIA'

b"Our inaugural Restaurant A380 opens its doors tomorrow at Singapore Changi Airport! Come dressed in your traditional heritage wear to receive a special gift from us! 

If you can't be there in person, join us on our Instagram Stories for our event coverage from 9am. Stay tuned! 

#DiscoverYourSIA"
b'Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! What well wishes will you find on the mooncakes you\xe2\x80\x99ll have tonight? Share them with us in the comments.'

b'Indulge in a taste of Singapore with this recipe from our Singapore Airlines chef. This broth is best enjoyed with a hot bowl of rice. Give it a go and show us your culinary creations! :cooked_rice::woman_cook::pot_of_food:'
b'What\xe2\x80\x99s inside the world\xe2\x80\x99s most beautiful buildings? Step into these glorious landmarks with us and make your next discovery.'

b"Laksa, one of Singapore's favourite delicacies, is inspired by a variety of Southeast Asian culture. This beautiful dish will test your skills, so remember to snap a picture of your success before digging in!"
b'Recreate our yogurt parfait with this healthy recipe by our Singapore Airlines chef. Tag us in your hearty breakfast shots! :airplane_selector::fork_and_knife_with_plate_selector:'
b'Spice up your happy hour at home with our Pineapple Ginger Turmeric Soda, specially created by our Singapore Airlines chef. Raise your glasses and make a toast! :airplane_selector::tropical_drink:'

b'From complimentary care kits to using technology to facilitate your travel, watch to learn what we are doing to ensure that you travel safely at every step of your journey. For more information, click the link on our profile #SIAcares'

b'As most of us around the world celebrate Eid from home this year, let\xe2\x80\x99s bask in the warmth that food and family bring. From our family to yours, Eid Mubarak!'
b'#StayHomewithSIA and keep your spirits up with our playlist, specially from us to you. \nFor this and other #KrisWorld playlists to listen to, visit SIA\xe2\x80\x99s Spotify page.'

b'Our thanks go out to frontline heroes such as those in healthcare and transport for their hard work and commitment during this Covid-19 outbreak. To support these amazing people, our Care, Transport and Contact Tracing Ambassadors are joining them on the ground. Together, we will emerge from this stronger because #WeAreInThisTogether. Read more about their experiences at https://bit.ly/2W8wj48'

b'The time will come when we will take to the skies again. For now, let\xe2\x80\x99s do what is best for our communities. Let\xe2\x80\x99s stay home and #KeepOurWingsUp #WeAreInThisTogether \n#WeAreAviation :airplane_selector:'

b"Shoutout to @flyscoot for tagging us. Yes the skies are a little grey, but let's keep our wings up.

Here\xe2\x80\x99s a beautiful moment captured by @akutsutomoyuki. Love is what flying feels like. Right now, we are staying strong at home. Looking forward to the day when all our planes can take to the skies again!

Nominating @aircanada @airnz @allnipponairways_official @flyingbrussels  @lufthansa @thaiairways to flood the social space with love and good vibes. #WeAreInThisTogether :airplane_selector:"

b'We\xe2\x80\x99re waiving all rebooking fees for tickets issued on or before 15 March 2020, for those with travel up to 31 May 2020. \nIf you purchased directly with us, please submit your request via our online Assistance Request Form at bit.ly/SIAAssistanceForm. For tickets purchased from a travel agency or through another airline, please get in touch with them directly. \nFor updates on Covid-19 travel information, kindly visit bit.ly/SIACovid19'
b"Double tap to share the love. Happy Valentine's Day :red_heart:"

b'We love how this very place is surrounded by beauty that dates back centuries. Each time you step into this city, this square will welcome you with its grand parades. Can you guess where we\xe2\x80\x99re flying to in October?'

b'When it comes to #SlowTravel in #Denmark, one of the \xe2\x80\x9crail\xe2\x80\x9d deals you have to experience is the train ride from #Copenhagen to #Aalborg \xe2\x80\x94 a city settled by Vikings over 1,000 years ago. \nRailway stations are located at the heart of every town and city in Europe. Looking for a local experience? Hop on!'
b'As we set the table for a joyful reunion, watch as these beautiful blooms brighten your Lunar New Year.'

b'Side dish or the life of the party? At the heart of Turkish cuisine is meze \xe2\x80\x94 a colourful line-up of hot and cold starters that often doubles as the main course when you\xe2\x80\x99re drinking with friends!'
b'Dine in. Eat out. Never shy away from food when you\xe2\x80\x99re in Beijing. There\xe2\x80\x99s more to this beautiful 3,000-year-old city than just Peking duck!'
